this auspicious day... we...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event216-01-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"... Phew... I think... I was able to say everything... smoothly... Although maybe I should review it once more...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event216-01-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"...? Company... this early?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event216-01-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"Morning~, Rin-rin! Sorry for coming by so suddenly.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event216-01-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"... It's okay... May I ask why though...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event216-01-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"You see, there's something I want to give you~... Here you go! Congrats on graduating!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event216-01-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"Wow... What a pretty bouquet... Thank you, Ako-chan... I'll take good care of it...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile06","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event216-01-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"You will?! Yay~! There's actually another reason I came though. I wanted to be the first one to congratulate you, but... were you busy or something?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event216-01-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"Don't worry... I was just rereading... my valedictory speech...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event216-01-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"Nice! It's so you to try to prepare perfectly right up to the very end!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event216-01-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"No... It's not that, Ako-chan... I'm just afraid I might become really nervous...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nnf01_openeye","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event216-01-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"Rin-rin...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event216-01-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"You'll be fine! You've gained so many levels from the super-duper hard work you put into all those challenges you took on!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event216-01-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"And even though this may be the last mission for your Student Council President final ascension class, I know you can do it!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event216-01-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"Last mission... It is... isn't it...? Alright... I'll go see things through to the very end...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event216-01-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"That's the spirit! It really stinks that I won't get to listen to your speech though~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event216-01-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"I imagine... Hina-san's valedictory speech... will be... quite the experience...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event216-01-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"Me too! The entrance ceremony was really fun, so it'll probably be something super unforgettable again!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event216-01-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"Fufu... I wouldn't be surprised... Anyway, we should probably head out... Let's go together until we have to part ways.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event216-01-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"Yeah, of course!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event216-01-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Hey~, Sis, have you seen my hanky~? The one with the alien on it~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event216-01-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"It's over here. That's why I told you to have everything ready yesterday. Mom ironed it for you, by the way.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event216-01-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Ehehe~, sorry~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event216-01-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"Seriously, Hina... Are you sure you're ready to make your valedictory speech?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"sigh01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event216-01-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Of course! I wrote and turned it in ages ago~! Oh~, but... it doesn't feel quite right anymore.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event216-01-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"What do you mean?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event216-01-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"When I wrote it, I was sure I'd written the best one I could, but I'm not so sure now... That's why I'll just talk about whatever I happen to be feeling during the speech!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event216-01-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"... You pulled that one during your entrance ceremony address. While I understand that Haneoka isn't strict, you shouldn't cause trouble for Hazawa-san and the faculty-","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event216-01-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Stop worrying so much~. Anyway, now that I have my hanky, let's go!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event216-01-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"Wait. Your necktie is a little crooked.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event216-01-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Really, it is? Fix it for me, please~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event216-01-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"Oh, fine... Come on and turn my way. And stand straight.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event216-01-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Okay~♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event216-01-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"... Don't forget to check your appearance in the mirror before you go up to speak. You have to look respectable as Haneoka's student council president.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event216-01-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"I know, I know~. I just kinda wanted you to fix my tie for me.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event216-01-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"Hmm?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event216-01-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"I mean, starting tomorrow, I won't be wearing a tie anymore, right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event216-01-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"... Yes, I suppose that's true. There. All good.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event216-01-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Thanks~! Oh, want me to check your ribbon for you? Never mind, yours is always nice and proper anyway~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event216-01-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"... Actually, please take a look, will you? How is it? Is it okay?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event216-01-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"... Mhm, just as I thought. Perfect as always!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event216-01-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"Alright, thank you.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event216-01-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Mmm~, I'm getting this fuzzy feeling in my chest! Let's hold hands today while we're going.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event216-01-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"You're going to be a college student soon, you know...? Well, just today.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event216-01-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Yay~! C'mon, let's go!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event216-01-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Yukina, do you have your handkerchief? What about tissues?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event216-01-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"Yes, I do. Here.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event216-01-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"That's it? You should bring a bit more. They might see some major action.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event216-01-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"You mean by you, right, Lisa?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event216-01-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Er... Ahaha~, that obvious?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event216-01-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"It doesn't exactly take a genius. You're going to do a lot of crying today anyway, aren't you...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event216-01-052","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Ahaha... Apologies in advance for the trouble...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event216-01-053","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"It's fine, I don't mind at all.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event216-01-054","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"Hina said your sadness comes from how much you treasure the people you've met at Haneoka... And I happen to be in agreement.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event216-01-055","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"So go ahead and cry as much as you want. After all, that's what today is for... Wait, Lisa, you...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event216-01-056","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"... Sniff... It's not my fault~. You're the one who said stuff that made me cry~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"cry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event216-01-057","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"That wasn't my intention... Here, use this.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event216-01-058","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Thanks.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event216-01-059","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"Fufu. Judging from what's already happening, I should probably do as you suggested and bring some extras.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event216-01-060","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"Okay, shall we go?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event216-01-061","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"What? We still have plenty of time. Can't we take things slow? You know what today is.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event216-01-062","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"That's exactly why... At least today, at the very end, I want to slowly walk along the route 